{"tid":424293,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"文學院毒男：新高登App完勝LIHKG","createTime":"2017-10-04T14:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T04:35:54.000Z","uid":6122,"like":25,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cd1a70dae28d5d56b5cbb9d5b274ba97c6e0b3f0","tid":424293,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"文學院毒男親自測試新高登App[black](並非指新加坡高登)[/black]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/212956_196bfef15f4f59910704519acca4db7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F212956_196bfef15f4f59910704519acca4db7b.jpg&h=257619e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n運行非常流暢<br />\n開post唔會有吹水台揀 出圖可選擇直接拍攝<br />\n有回帶、留名功能<br />\n可選icon數量完勝<br />\n睇post可選3種界面：冇（若有圖片）preview、有preview、標題變成圖片caption並只列出有圖post<br />\n起底可瀏覽用戶回覆，而非只有出嘅post<br />\n選台介面稍輸<br />\n搜尋仍然無法搜舊post<br />\n未有pm、追蹤中功能<br />\n封測暫無廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議各位親身體驗<br />\n<br />\n總結：LIHKG=香港，高登=新加坡<br />\n前者大勢已去，日漸凋零<br />\n後者蒸蒸日上，欣欣向榮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n回老家吧<br />\nbalik kampung<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62937beea9d56484f3662d946f0a592989ee9b2a","tid":424293,"uid":1567,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:25:27.000Z","msg":"麻煩連尼住block左呢個post, thanks"},{"pid":"b8166aa6a5ac79307bfc0a6db59a26f87da4376f","tid":424293,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麻煩連尼住block左呢個post, thanks</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d9d3adb0ede6d0291f21473e5306a6887dcc57","tid":424293,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:27:55.000Z","msg":"好用有咩用 有人上先得咖"